@startuml
title AI Response Sequence
participant ChatApplicationService
participant AiContextBudgetManager
participant AiServicePort
participant Provider
ChatApplicationService -> AiContextBudgetManager : budget(AiRequest)
AiContextBudgetManager --> ChatApplicationService : bounded request/result
ChatApplicationService -> AiServicePort : generateResponse
AiServicePort -> Provider : provider API/local call
Provider --> AiServicePort : response/failure
AiServicePort --> ChatApplicationService : AiResponse
@enduml
